{"tid":1631891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士狗鄭生 還腳呀","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:31.000Z","uid":92299,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d88cc28af8ee2512f1e206537e26b488c89206","tid":1631891,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"你依家係同全香港人宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e459779175ed2ad07ac40a5c767ed8dd17f46c21","tid":1631891,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8fd2d7032bf5021884fe83d08ab72b35c8eb2f0","tid":1631891,"uid":46271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"阻膠死全家"},{"pid":"618d19d9379939b0cf5c843beca37a2e703fb86f","tid":1631891,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"阻膠再阻人 唔好怪人私了埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799c4019cfb2b3914000dc1f010855d392c32cf6","tid":1631891,"uid":148262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n還腳！"},{"pid":"495c5f37bad2c01782f0d13688141f79e46bc5ba","tid":1631891,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"佢危殆中"},{"pid":"ba0cd92cfbc27c990acbee9fd0beb731791c62bc","tid":1631891,"uid":214940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"打到佢手腳俱廢，兼閹撚埋佢。要佢求生不得，求死不能，累鳩死佢屋企人。<br />\n咁先還到我女手足嘅血海深仇嘅萬分之一。<br />\n死？太便宜佢啦<br />\n好撚柒嬲啊屌佢老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3be3ccbec8d1e93f83075dddf65471890a82a53","tid":1631891,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osbDDvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosbDDvg.jpg&h=e4f7b390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab337a5cba855cfa854f7a5f8e834a7d6bf854ec","tid":1631891,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"的士狗 呢個仇 香港人一定會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f4f6b55322f20c350d1bb4dc5a951c97e3f603","tid":1631891,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3be3ccbec8d1e93f83075dddf65471890a82a53","tid":1631891,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osbDDvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosbDDvg.jpg&h=e4f7b390&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母鄭國泉，化撚左灰都認得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd0a940c3a3fb6986b9398b940003f5f8e6d846","tid":1631891,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"2076300065c8379a1b9f94e8b76753a791446d82","tid":1631891,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"495c5f37bad2c01782f0d13688141f79e46bc5ba","tid":1631891,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"佢危殆中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"死左先講"},{"pid":"66ddb9212c1d9c43bb76576468e3970ccd288fa5","tid":1631891,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495c5f37bad2c01782f0d13688141f79e46bc5ba","tid":1631891,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"佢危殆中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"有無source.<br />\n之前有人話佢出左院"},{"pid":"ac2e2d007be7522714271b3e0c73baa4503dec9a","tid":1631891,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ddb9212c1d9c43bb76576468e3970ccd288fa5","tid":1631891,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495c5f37bad2c01782f0d13688141f79e